{
  "title": "3. Peygamberimizin Yanında Yetişen Gençler",
  "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"tr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Peygamberimizin Yanında Yetişen Gençler</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marcellus&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap');\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f3f4f6;\n            color: #1f2937;\n        }\n\n        .header-font {\n            font-family: 'Marcellus', serif;\n        }\n\n        .hero-pattern {\n            background-color: #065f46;\n            background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23047857' fill-opacity='0.4'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E\");\n        }\n\n        .card-transition {\n            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);\n        }\n\n        .card-transition:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .scroll-smooth {\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"scroll-smooth\">\n\n    <!-- Hero Section -->\n    <header class=\"hero-pattern text-white min-h-[300px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center p-8 relative shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-20\"></div>\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl\">\n            <span class=\"bg-yellow-500 text-emerald-900 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide mb-4 inline-block\">2. Ünite</span>\n            <h1 class=\"header-font text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight\">Peygamberimizin Yanında Yetişen Gençler</h1>\n            <p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-emerald-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto italic\">\n                \"Karanlıktan Aydınlığa: Bir Rehberin İzinde Değişen Hayatlar\"\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-12 -mt-10 relative z-20\">\n\n        <!-- Introduction: Why Did Youth Choose Him? -->\n        <section class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-12 border-l-8 border-emerald-600\">\n            <h2 class=\"header-font text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-question-circle mr-3 text-yellow-600\"></i>\n                Gençler Neden Hz. Peygamber'e Koştu?\n            </h2>\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                <div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                        Cahiliye döneminde gençler, adaletsizlik ve değer görmeme gibi sorunlarla boğuşuyordu. Hz. Muhammed (sav) onlara sadece bir din değil, aynı zamanda <strong>değer, sorumluluk ve kimlik</strong> sundu.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-emerald-500 mr-2\"></i> Sorgulamaya teşvik etmesi</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-emerald-500 mr-2\"></i> Yeteneklerine göre görev vermesi</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-check text-emerald-500 mr-2\"></i> Baskılara karşı onlara güvenmesi</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-center\">\n                    <div>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-users text-4xl text-emerald-300 mb-2\"></i>\n                        <p class=\"font-bold text-emerald-800\">\"İslam davetine koşanların çoğu gençlerden oluşmuştur.\"</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- The Young Companions Grid -->\n        <h2 class=\"header-font text-3xl text-center text-gray-800 mb-8 font-bold\">Öncü Genç Sahabiler</h2>\n        \n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16\">\n\n            <!-- Musab bin Umeyr -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-indigo-600 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Musab bin Umeyr</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher text-indigo-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 uppercase mb-2\">İslam'ın İlk Öğretmeni</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Zengin bir ailenin çocuğu olmasına rağmen her şeyden vazgeçti. Medine'ye öğretmen olarak gönderildi ve şehrin İslam'a hazırlanmasını sağladı.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Fedakarlık & Tebliğ\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Cafer bin Ebu Talib -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-600 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Cafer bin Ebu Talib</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-ship text-blue-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase mb-2\">Habeşistan Lideri</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Habeşistan'a hicret eden kafilenin genç lideri. Kral Necaşi'nin huzurunda İslam'ı korkusuzca ve hikmetle savundu.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Cesaret & Hitabet\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Üsame bin Zeyd -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-red-600 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Üsame bin Zeyd</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-flag text-red-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-2\">Genç Komutan</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Henüz 18 yaşındayken, içlerinde yaşlı sahabilerin de bulunduğu orduya Hz. Peygamber tarafından komutan olarak atandı.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Liyakat & Liderlik\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Hz. Zeyneb -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-pink-600 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Hz. Zeyneb</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-heart text-pink-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-pink-600 uppercase mb-2\">Sabır Timsali</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Eşi inanmamasına rağmen inancından vazgeçmedi. Nazik ve sabırlı tutumuyla eşinin sonradan Müslüman olmasına vesile oldu.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Sabır & Nezaket\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Abdullah bin Ömer -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-amber-500 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Abdullah bin Ömer</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-scroll text-amber-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-600 uppercase mb-2\">İlim ve Dikkat</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Peygamberi gölge gibi takip eder, her hareketini gözlemlerdi. En çok hadis rivayet eden sahabilerden biri oldu.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Gözlem & İlim\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Nesîbe (Ümmü Ümare) -->\n            <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-transition border border-gray-100\">\n                <div class=\"bg-emerald-600 h-2\"></div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\">\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-800\">Nesîbe (ra)</h3>\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt text-emerald-500 text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase mb-2\">Kahraman Hanım</p>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4\">\n                        Uhud Savaşı'nda eşi ve oğluyla birlikte Hz. Peygamber'e siper oldu. Cesaretiyle Hz. Peygamber'in övgüsünü kazandı.\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-500 border border-gray-200\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-tag mr-1\"></i> Cesaret & Sadakat\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Interactive Story / Empathy Section -->\n        <section class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-12 shadow-2xl\">\n            <div class=\"md:flex items-center gap-8\">\n                <div class=\"md:w-1/2 mb-6 md:mb-0\">\n                    <h3 class=\"header-font text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-yellow-400\">Düşün ve Tamamla: \"Bilge Genç\"</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-300 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed\">\n                        \"Uzak bir şehre giden bir genç, oradaki haksızlıkları görür ve düzeltmeye karar verir...\"\n                    </p>\n                    <div class=\"bg-gray-700 bg-opacity-50 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-yellow-500\">\n                        <p class=\"italic text-sm\">\"Sen o gencin yerinde olsaydın, insanlara doğruyu anlatmak için önce nereden başlardın?\"</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"md:w-1/2\">\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2\">Empati Köşesi</h4>\n                    <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                        <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                            <span class=\"bg-emerald-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded mr-3 mt-1\">Soru 1</span>\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">Zor durumda olan ve sığınacak yeri olmayan birine (Habeşistan örneği) nasıl yardım edersin?</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                            <span class=\"bg-emerald-600 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded mr-3 mt-1\">Soru 2</span>\n                            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">Ailen veya arkadaşların doğru bildiğin bir şeyden seni vazgeçirmeye çalışsa (Musab örneği) tavrın ne olurdu?</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Footer -->\n        <footer class=\"text-center text-gray-500 text-sm pb-8\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 Din Kültürü ve Ahlak Bilgisi Dersi Materyali</p>\n            <p class=\"mt-2 text-xs\">Kaynak: 9. Sınıf Ders Kitabı, 2. Ünite</p>\n        </footer>\n\n    </main>\n</body>\n</html>"
}